    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, running like a total charm! It's perfect if you're looking for something dependable that still looks great pulling into the driveway. I've taken good care of it, and it's officially ready for its next big adventure. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great home!",
