    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain is bolstered by a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. This example has undergone proactive maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed VANOS system to ensure timing precision. The suspension maintains its factory-tuned balance with MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup, offering the communicative chassis feedback these cars are known for. Minor cosmetic patina is present, consistent with its age, but it remains mechanically robust and ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
