      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. Finished in a classic deep metallic paint that still holds a brilliant shine, the exterior shows only minor signs of road use consistent with a well-loved car. Inside, the premium upholstery has been treated regularly, remaining supple and free of tears, though light creasing is visible on the driver\u2019s bolster. Mechanically, it is in excellent health; I have kept a comprehensive folder of all service records, including recent fluid flushes and a fresh set of high-performance tires. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts with precision. It\u2019s a turn-key example ready for its next owner who appreciates a car that has been cared for by a detail-oriented enthusiast.",
      "price": 36500.0,
